These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: january, march, november, february, september, july
There are 6 different favourite colors: azure, blue, mauve, apricot, amber, red
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
2. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes red##1
6. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
8. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Birthday   | july | january  | november    | february  | march      | september    |
| Color      | blue  | red | amber | azure | apricot | mauve |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
6 different games are played: monopoly, billiard, poker, go, scrabble, canasta
There are 6 different favourite colors: amber, light-blue, mauve, ivory, black, blood-red
1. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes black##1
2. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person playing go##1
3. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
4. the person who likes mauve is on the far left##1
5. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
6. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
7. the person playing canasta is the person who likes blood-red##1
8. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
9. the person playing monopoly is the person who likes mauve##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Game   | monopoly   | scrabble | billiard | canasta | go     | poker  |
| Color           | mauve | light-blue    | amber      | blood-red  | ivory | black |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: coral, aquamarine, green, blue, fuchsia, mauve
House: art-deco, wooden, gothic-revival, cape-cod, palace, modern
1. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
2. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
3. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
4. the person who likes green is on the right of the palace house##1
5. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the modern house##1
6. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the wooden house##1
7. the cape-cod house is on the far right##1
8. the gothic-revival house is the person who likes blue##1
9. the person who likes green is the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Color   | blue   | mauve   | fuchsia      | aquamarine | coral  | green   |
| House   | gothic-revival | modern | art-deco | wooden   | palace | cape-cod |

