.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, game, alhambra, prince, chaman, cain
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: family, scientific, time-travel, superhero, disaster, spy
1. the person watching family movies is on the far left##1
2. the alhambra-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
4. the cain-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
5. the person watching spy movies is the prince-smoker##1
6. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
7. the chaman-smoker is on the far right##1
8. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| Cigar   | alhambra  | prince | montecristo      | game  | cain | chaman |
| Movie-Genre     | family | spy  | disaster | time-travel | superhero  | scientific    |

