.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, soy-milk, sprite, fanta, hot-chocolate
There 6 different types of food: lemon, garlic, pineapple, tomato, apple, corn
 1. the person eating pineapple is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
 3. the person eating apple is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 4. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
 5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 6. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
 9. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
10. the person drinking sprite is the person eating corn##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Beverage         | sprite | hot-chocolate | almond-milk | fanta | cola | soy-milk  |
| Food   | corn  | tomato  | pineapple  | lemon | apple      | garlic |

