.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-6::.
6 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, bird, ferret, cat, pony, frog
City: new-york, paris, hamburg, berlin, san-francisco, boston
1. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
4. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is the owner of the frog##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
7. the person traveling to new-york is on the far right##1
8. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
9. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Pet   | frog    | ferret    | guinea-pig | pony     | bird   | cat     |
| City   | san-francisco | paris | boston | hamburg | berlin | new-york |

