4. the game-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
5. the chaman-smoker is the chef##1
6. the game-smoker is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
7. the police-officer is on the right of the chef##1
8. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| Job   | chef | police-officer  | electrician     | doctor    | designer  | mechanic          |
| Cigar         | chaman  | fonseca | game | dunhill | siglo | bluemaster |

