.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-9::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: cricket, baseball, climbing, parkour, weightlifting, volleyball
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: december, april, july, september, august, june
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who's sport is cricket##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
9. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |    3     |   4    |       5       |     6      |
| Sport    | weightlifting | baseball | parkour | volleyball    | cricket | climbing      |
| Birthday   | july   | december     | april      | august | june           | september |

