.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-10::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: sprite, cola, coffee, hot-chocolate, lemonade, mirinda
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, montecristo, siglo, fonseca, vegafina, alhambra
1. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
3. the montecristo-smoker is the person drinking cola##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
5. the fonseca-smoker is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is the chaman-smoker##1
8. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
9. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Beverage          | cola | mirinda   | lemonade  | coffee    | hot-chocolate  | sprite |
| Cigar   | montecristo   | chaman | alhambra | vegafina | siglo | fonseca |

