.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-11::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, blend, baccarat, vegafina, cain, bongani
The people use 6 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, bike, taxi, skateboard, quad-bike
1. the blend-smoker is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
3. the bongani-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
5. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1
7. the ritmeester-smoker is the person driving the taxi##1
8. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
9. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |   3   |      4      |    5     |     6     |
| Cigar   | bongani    | ritmeester     | baccarat | blend | vegafina | cain   |
| Transport        | quad-bike | taxi | skateboard | bike   | bus    | motorbike |

