.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-12::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: techno, pop, funk, jazz, dubstep, soul
There are 6 different favourite beverages: water, milk, cola, lemonade, almond-milk, soy-milk
1. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
2. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of pop##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is the fan of jazz##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
6. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
7. the fan of funk is on the left of the person drinking water##1
8. the person drinking milk is on the left of the fan of soul##1
9. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |    5    |    6    |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | soul | jazz    | pop | funk  | techno |
| Beverage     | milk    | almond-milk | lemonade | soy-milk   | cola | water    |

