.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-20::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: milk, lemonade, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, 7up, tea
City: colone, new-york, marseilles, berlin, nizza, edinburgh
1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
7. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
8. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
9. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |     3      |   4    |   5   |     6      |
| Beverage   | lemonade | tea     | 7up       | hot-chocolate  | almond-milk | milk    |
| City     | edinburgh  | colone | new-york | berlin | nizza  | marseilles |

 